imdb.plot outline: In the Solar System, The First Interplanetary War ends up with the supremacy of a communist party on Earth and its strong pressure and influence on Mars, Venus and the United States of Jupiter politics. The Earth left the Moon out of resources and full of brothels and mafia gangs and now, a big company is financing a scientist to build a strictly classified object with an innovative antimatter technology that can ease the interplanetary colonization for the planet that owns it. That is the reason why the mafia and the governments of the other planets are getting more and more worried. So, Whiskey and Atreia, the spy-daughter of the martian president are sent on Earth by the martian mafia in search of an interplanetary spaceship that will help them steal the mysterious object. Meanwhile, the martian president, Victor Dynamix declares Mars independence to Earth. Whiskey and Atreia befriend Grasul, a First Interplanetary War veteran and the Robot. Their plans for recovering their spaceship are prevented and they have to face some quite serious obstacles to get it back. They finally manage to seize it, but a space fleet from Earth is now attacking Mars.
imdb.title: Planetar
plot: Four martians team up to retrieve a special object that can cause social and political mayhem in the Solar System.::Bogdan Nedelcu
